sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    participant Runtime as Sandbox container entrypoint
    participant Config as YAML config and identity
    participant State as /state version-4 stores
    participant Outbox as Durable startup event outbox
    participant Manager as sandbox-manager protocol session
    participant Setup as Preflight and setup adapters
    participant Daemon as SandboxDaemon / host runtime

    Runtime->>Config: Resolve sandboxId, instanceId, paths, and config path
    Runtime->>Config: Load and strictly validate YAML configuration
    Config-->>Runtime: Typed config and config digest
    Runtime->>State: Validate version-4 layout and acquire state lock
    Runtime->>State: Load idempotency, outbox, ACK, status, and connectivity
    Runtime->>State: Recover journals, tasks, checkpoints, and unacked events
    State-->>Runtime: Initialized stores and recovered state
    Runtime->>Outbox: Attach StartupReporter durable event sink
    Runtime->>Daemon: Construct boot-only daemon
    Runtime->>Manager: Start protocol client and connect early
    Manager-->>Runtime: welcome / accepted resume cursor
    Runtime->>Manager: ready(status = booting)
    Note over Runtime,Manager: The controller connects before lengthy setup so boot progress can stream live.

    Runtime->>Setup: Filesystem/runtime preflight
    Setup-->>Runtime: Mount, permission, and policy result
    Runtime->>Setup: Resolve model catalog/runtime
    Setup-->>Runtime: Active model and optional degraded status
    Runtime->>Setup: Build secret-store registry and resolver
    Setup-->>Runtime: Secret-store availability metadata (never values)
    Runtime->>Setup: Configure Git identity and credentials
    Setup-->>Runtime: Git setup result and secure environment
    Runtime->>Setup: Authenticate GitHub access
    Setup-->>Runtime: GitHub setup result
    Runtime->>Setup: Load project context files
    Setup-->>Runtime: Context descriptors
    Runtime->>Setup: Load available skills
    Setup-->>Runtime: Skill descriptors
    Runtime->>Setup: Execute configured boot phases
    Setup-->>Runtime: Persisted attempts and bounded/redacted logs
    Runtime->>Daemon: initializeRuntime(setup, skills, context, model, secrets)
    Daemon->>State: Compose tools, tasks, Git, harness, explore, and runs
    Daemon->>State: Recover interrupted active work
    Daemon-->>Runtime: Runtime initialized

    loop Every startup stage and status change
        Runtime->>Outbox: Append typed durable startup event
        alt Manager session is connected
            Outbox->>Manager: Deliver sandbox:<id> event
            Manager-->>Outbox: Processed ACK after durable ingestion
        else Manager session is disconnected
            Note over Outbox: Retain event in /state/events/outbox.jsonl for reconnect replay
        end
    end

    alt Config changed during recovery or model runtime is limited
        Runtime->>Daemon: markReady(degraded)
        Runtime->>Outbox: Append sandbox.ready(status = degraded, limitations)
        Runtime->>Manager: Protocol ready / status update (degraded)
    else Fully ready
        Runtime->>Daemon: markReady(ready)
        Runtime->>Outbox: Append sandbox.ready(status = ready)
        Runtime->>Manager: Protocol ready / status update (ready)
    end

    Note over Runtime,State: /state remains the file-first source of truth for setup, run/task state,<br/>outbox/ACK, idempotency, checkpoints, and caches.
    Note over Runtime,Manager: On controller disconnect, the configured policy governs reconnect/self-exit.<br/>Where omitted, exit_self defaults to 300 seconds. Exit code 22 means reconnecting.
